						<summary>

						<p>Registers the gift of 15 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold also referred to as <hi rend="italic">Varāha-gajjāṇam</hi> to Varamtarumperumāḷdāsar towards a garland to be offered daily to god for the merit of <hi rend="bold">Kāmadēva,</hi> son of <hi rend="bold">Tikkāṉai Nāchchiyār, a queen of Vīra Sōmēśvara.</hi> The details of the date viz., the <hi rend="bold">32nd regnal year,</hi> Tulā, ba. 7, Monday, Pūśam correspond to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1247, October 22, Tuesday (not Monday); ·20, ·1�.</hi></p>						

