<lb n="7" break="no"/>(ka)ḷum Ivarkaḷ va<hi rend="grantha">rgga</hi>ttārum <hi rend="grantha">candrāditya</hi>varai nāḷonṟukku Oru tirumālai Eṭukkak kaṭavatākavum niccai
<lb n="8" break="no"/>yittatu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Itu <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>vai<hi rend="grantha">ṣṇa</hi>varkaḷ ra<hi rend="grantha">kṣai <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi>
